---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import { Icon } from "astro-icon/components";
---

<Layout title="404 · 传感器连接中断">
  <section class="min-h-[70vh] flex items-center justify-center py-20 px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 bg-brand-yellow-light noise-overlay">
    <div class="max-w-xl w-full text-center">
      <!-- 404 Bold Mono Display -->
      <div class="inline-flex bg-brand-black text-brand-yellow border-4 border-brand-black p-6 rounded-3xl shadow-md rotate-[-2deg] mb-8 relative select-none">
        <span class="text-7xl sm:text-8xl font-mono font-black tracking-widest leading-none">404</span>
        <div class="absolute -top-3.5 -right-3.5 bg-brand-red text-white border-2 border-brand-black px-2.5 py-0.5 rounded text-[10px] font-mono font-bold uppercase rotate-[15deg]">
          OFFLINE
        </div>
      </div>

      <h1 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-black text-brand-black mb-4">
        传感器连接中断 / 找不到该路由
      </h1>
      
      <p class="text-sm sm:text-base text-gray-700 leading-relaxed max-w-md mx-auto mb-10">
        哎呀！系统没能在当前端口上读取到任何有效数据。可能该路径尚未组装完毕，或者发生了硬件接触不良。
      </p>

      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center items-center">
        <a
          href="/courses"
          class="focus-ring inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 px-6 py-3.5 bg-brand-black text-white font-bold rounded-lg hover:bg-brand-graphite transition-all active:scale-95 shadow-sm cursor-pointer w-full sm:w-auto"
        >
          <Icon name="lucide:cpu" class="w-4 h-4 text-brand-yellow" />
          浏览课程矩阵
        </a>
        <a
          href="/"
          class="focus-ring inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 px-6 py-3.5 bg-white text-brand-black border-2 border-brand-black font-bold rounded-lg hover:bg-brand-yellow-light transition-all active:scale-95 shadow-sm cursor-pointer w-full sm:w-auto"
        >
          <Icon name="lucide:compass" class="w-4 h-4 text-brand-red" />
          返回网站首页
        </a>
      </div>
      
      <p class="text-[10px] font-mono text-brand-black/40 mt-12">
        ERROR_CODE: 0x404_ROUTER_LOST · CHAIHUO ACADEMY OS v2.2
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
